features: High Quality Materials: Our desk bookshelf is made of MDF wood with smooth and high gloss finish, durable, waterproof, and easy to clean without fading. Desk bookshelf won’t be decayed or damaged.There is no irritating smell. The bolts would never scratch the books.

Size: Our small tree bookshelf is 16(H) x 12.2(L) x 6.7(W) inches,very compact and comes with 5 panels and 3 shelves design. Each shelf can be loaded with up to 5-10 books, beautiful solid wooden shelves that are perfect for displaying your books, magazines, decorations, novels, speakers etc.

Wide Applications: This book tree bookshelf have 3 open shelves, suitable for any room that needs a bookcase or display desktop bookshelf and is not only a beautiful work of art, but also a practical bookshelf organizer for living room, office, bedroom, studio, study room, lounge, bookstore and library etc.

Fine Design: The desktop tree bookshelf is an old-time classic with a charming vintage look and functional design. match perfectly with any other furniture in your home.It takes full advantage of your desktop space and keep your desktop clear. Desk bookshelf can be adjusted to the size of your desktop to Save Space. Change the angle to fit your needs.

Easy To Install: 3 tier tree bookshelf comes with included clear and detailed instructions, numbered parts, and a L shaped allen wrench for assembly, tree bookshelf can be easily completed in about 5 minutes. The shelves can easily be cleaned with a wet rag.
